{
  "texts": [
    "The hybridization of fuzzy soft sets and N-soft sets led [18] to define fuzzy N-soft sets.",
    "[99] contributed with the multifuzzy N-soft set model that extends the multi-fuzzy soft set notion defined by [237].",
    "In addition, N-soft sets were amplified with the help of hesitancy too.",
    "This was a remarkable improvement, because hesitancy in the strict framework of soft sets reduced to producing incomplete soft sets.",
    "The extension that emerged was called hesitant Nsoft set in [19]."
  ]
}